This paper deals with the Degrees of Freedom (DoF) of a multi-antenna interference channel with a relay, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of a relay also involves networked communication (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses linear transmission strategies, which are related to machine learning and optimization (cs.MM) and communication engineering (cs.CE).
